001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 65,
009    displayName = "Bolus Requested 2/3",
010    usedByAndroid = true,
011    usedByTidepool = true
012)
013public class BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
014    
015    private int bolusId;
016    private int options;
017    private int standardPercent;
018    private int duration;
019    private int spare1;
020    private int isf;
021    private int targetBG;
022    private boolean userOverride;
023    private boolean declinedCorrection;
024    private int selectedIOB;
025    private int spare2;
026    
027    public BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog() {}
028    
029    public BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int options, int standardPercent, int duration, int spare1, int isf, int targetBG, boolean userOverride, boolean declinedCorrection, int selectedIOB, int spare2) {
030        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, bolusId, options, standardPercent, duration, spare1, isf, targetBG, userOverride, declinedCorrection, selectedIOB, spare2);
031        this.pumpTimeSec = pumpTimeSec;
032        this.sequenceNum = sequenceNum;
033        this.bolusId = bolusId;
034        this.options = options;
035        this.standardPercent = standardPercent;
036        this.duration = duration;
037        this.spare1 = spare1;
038        this.isf = isf;
039        this.targetBG = targetBG;
040        this.userOverride = userOverride;
041        this.declinedCorrection = declinedCorrection;
042        this.selectedIOB = selectedIOB;
043        this.spare2 = spare2;
044    }
045
046    public BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog(int bolusId, int options, int standardPercent, int duration, int spare1, int isf, int targetBG, boolean userOverride, boolean declinedCorrection, int selectedIOB, int spare2) {
047        this(0, 0, bolusId, options, standardPercent, duration, spare1, isf, targetBG, userOverride, declinedCorrection, selectedIOB, spare2);
048    }
049
050    public int typeId() {
051        return 65;
052    }
053
054    /**
055     * <table border="1">
056     * <caption>Parsed fields for BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog:</caption>
057     * <tr><td><code>bolusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
058     * <tr><td><code>options</code></td><td><code>raw[12]</code></td></tr>
059     * <tr><td><code>standardPercent</code></td><td><code>raw[13]</code></td></tr>
060     * <tr><td><code>duration</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
061     * <tr><td><code>spare1</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
062     * <tr><td><code>isf</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
063     * <tr><td><code>targetBG</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 20)</code></td></tr>
064     * <tr><td><code>userOverride</code></td><td><code>raw[22] != 0</code></td></tr>
065     * <tr><td><code>declinedCorrection</code></td><td><code>raw[23] != 0</code></td></tr>
066     * <tr><td><code>selectedIOB</code></td><td><code>raw[24]</code></td></tr>
067     * <tr><td><code>spare2</code></td><td><code>raw[1]</code></td></tr>
068     * </table>
069     */
070    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
071        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
072        this.cargo = raw;
073        parseBase(raw);
074        this.bolusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
075        this.options = raw[12];
076        this.standardPercent = raw[13];
077        this.duration = Bytes.readShort(raw, 14);
078        this.spare1 = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
079        this.isf = Bytes.readShort(raw, 18);
080        this.targetBG = Bytes.readShort(raw, 20);
081        this.userOverride = raw[22] != 0;
082        this.declinedCorrection = raw[23] != 0;
083        this.selectedIOB = raw[24];
084        this.spare2 = raw[1];
085        
086    }
087
088    
089    /**
090     * <table border="1">
091     * <caption>Byte layout for BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
092     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
093     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{(byte) 65} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
094     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
095     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
096     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
097     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
098     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
099     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
100     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
101     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
102     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
103     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
104     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
105     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>(byte) options</code></td></tr>
106     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>(byte) standardPercent</code></td></tr>
107     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(duration) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
108     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(duration) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
109     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare1) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
110     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare1) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
111     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(isf) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
112     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(isf) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
113     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(targetBG) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
114     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(targetBG) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
115     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>(byte) (userOverride ? 1 : 0)</code></td></tr>
116     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>(byte) (declinedCorrection ? 1 : 0)</code></td></tr>
117     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>(byte) selectedIOB</code></td></tr>
118     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>(byte) spare2</code></td></tr>
119     * </table>
120     */
121    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int options, int standardPercent, int duration, int spare1, int isf, int targetBG, boolean userOverride, boolean declinedCorrection, int selectedIOB, int spare2) {
122        return Bytes.combine(
123            new byte[] { (byte) 65, 0},
124            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
125            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
126            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId), 
127            new byte[]{ (byte) options }, 
128            new byte[]{ (byte) standardPercent }, 
129            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(duration), 
130            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare1), 
131            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(isf), 
132            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(targetBG), 
133            new byte[]{ (byte) (userOverride ? 1 : 0) }, 
134            new byte[]{ (byte) (declinedCorrection ? 1 : 0) }, 
135            new byte[]{ (byte) selectedIOB }, 
136            new byte[]{ (byte) spare2 });
137    }
138
139    /**
140     * @return bolus ID
141     */
142    public int getBolusId() {
143        return bolusId;
144    }
145    public int getOptions() {
146        return options;
147    }
148
149    /**
150     * @return 100 if a standard bolus, otherwise the percent of the bolus which is performed up
151     * front in an extended bolus
152     */
153    public int getStandardPercent() {
154        return standardPercent;
155    }
156
157    /**
158     * @return 0 if a standard bolus, otherwise the duration between the standard and extended bolus
159     */
160    public int getDuration() {
161        return duration;
162    }
163
164    public int getSpare1() {
165        return spare1;
166    }
167
168    /**
169     * @return insulin sensitivity factor in the insulin delivery profile
170     */
171    public int getIsf() {
172        return isf;
173    }
174
175    /**
176     * @return target BG in mg/dL in the insulin delivery profile
177     */
178    public int getTargetBG() {
179        return targetBG;
180    }
181
182    /**
183     * @return true if the user overrode the insulin delivery amount (i.e., not calculated just
184     * from the combination of carbs + BG correction)
185     */
186    public boolean getUserOverride() {
187        return userOverride;
188    }
189
190    /**
191     * @return true if the correction amount due to the current BG+IOB was declined
192     */
193    public boolean getDeclinedCorrection() {
194        return declinedCorrection;
195    }
196
197    /**
198     * @return TODO(unknown)
199     */
200    public int getSelectedIOB() {
201        return selectedIOB;
202    }
203    public int getSpare2() {
204        return spare2;
205    }
206
